# Gano Digital — Cursor Rules (2026-04-06)
# Instrucciones personalizadas para coherencia Reseller + API strategy

## PRODUCT MODEL

Canonical checkout: GoDaddy Reseller Store + RCC (WordPress vitrina)
API: Developer Portal REST (opcional, backend automation ONLY)
Good as Gold: Solo API purchases (debita prepago). No requerido para consultas.

Decision: Checkout? → RCC. Backend automation? → API (env vars). Comprar vía API? → Good as Gold check.

## WORDPRESS SECURITY (SIEMPRE)

✅ Nonce: wp_verify_nonce($_POST['nonce'], 'action')
✅ Sanitize: sanitize_text_field(), sanitize_email(), sanitize_textarea_field()
✅ Escape: esc_html(), esc_attr(), esc_url(), esc_js()
✅ Rate limit: set_transient('rl_' . md5($ip), 1, 60)
✅ MU plugin: lógica crítica, nunca en tema

❌ Eval, SQL directo, hardcode secrets, jQuery

## RESELLER & PFID

PFID constants: define('GANO_PFID_HOSTING_ECONOMIA', 'PENDING_RCC')
NO hardcode domain IDs (crear issue "RCC: Obtener PFIDs")
Cart URL: gano_rstore_cart_url($pfid) helper

## CODE PATTERNS

PHP Form:
function gano_contact_submit() {
  check_admin_referer('gano_contact', 'nonce');
  $email = sanitize_email($_POST['email']);
  if (!is_email($email)) wp_die('Invalid');
  wp_mail($admin, 'Contacto', $msg, $headers);
  wp_redirect(home_url('/gracias')); exit;
}

JavaScript (vanilla):
const input = document.getElementById('gano-chat-input');
input?.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
  fetch(ganoChatConfig.endpoint, {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: { 'X-Nonce': ganoChatConfig.nonce },
    body: JSON.stringify({ query: e.target.value.trim() })
  }).then(r => r.json()).catch(err => console.error(err));
});

CSS (tokens):
:root { --gano-gold: #D4AF37; --gano-orange: #FF8C42; }
.gano-btn { background: var(--gano-orange); padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; }

## MISTAKES

API para checkout → RCC canonical
Hardcode tokens → [REDACTED] o env vars
Olvidar nonce → wp_nonce_field() + verify
Magic PFID → Constantes en functions.php

## QUICK CHECKLIST

□ Checkout? → RCC only
□ API call? → Server-side, env vars
□ Form? → Nonce + sanitize + rate limit
□ Secret? → .env.local, NO commit
□ CSS? → Tokens
□ JS? → Vanilla, NO jQuery
□ Ready? → Security checklist

